parameters: Flora: "Is this a magic shop, I wonder...?"
Magic Shop Owner Marion: "I'm Marion. The owner of this magic shop."

Magic Shop Owner Marion: "Here you can purchase grimoires and create
scrolls in the room over there."

Magic Shop Manager Lala: "Also, if you have any grimoires you don't
need anymore, just drop them in that postbox. You'll get about half
your money back for recycling them, so it's a really good deal."

Marion, the owner of the Magic Shop: "Welcome~ Feel free to ask if
there's anything you want~"
Marion, the owner of the Magic Shop: "Welcome~"
Marion, the owner of the Magic Shop: "Thank you very much~"
